00:18:27,670 --> 00:18:32,820
By the way, did you get
your fiancé killed again?

263
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:36,910
Too close!

264
00:18:36,910 --> 00:18:39,930
Why do you keep asking me that?
You're so annoying!

265
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:42,700
Annoying but?

266
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:46,800
Annoying but what? Hmmm?

267
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:43,830
--Too close!

268
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:51,140
Annoying but you like me, maybe?

269
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:54,350
That's enough!
Young Master-sama was calling you!

270
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:56,630
Young Master-sama?

271
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:59,070
He wanted you to bring that thing!

272
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,850
Stay away! You make me sick!

273
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:02,650
Hey, hey, hey!

274
00:19:02,650 --> 00:19:06,590
You just keep getting your fiancé killed! Baby 5!

275
00:19:06,590 --> 00:19:12,030
Stop choosing guys that would
be killed by Doffy and marry me!

276
00:19:23,690 --> 00:19:26,110
Hmm, just kidding!

277
00:19:30,650 --> 00:19:32,260
Do you...

278
00:19:32,770 --> 00:19:34,190
...need me?

279
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,320
Cut it out!

280
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:41,790
The Colosseum is always packed.

281
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:45,460
Thanks to you, Diamante.

282
00:19:45,990 --> 00:19:47,320
What are you saying?

283
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:51,950
Doffy, that's because
you're a charismatic king.

284
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:53,740
No.

285
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:57,980
That's because you're strong.

286
00:19:57,980 --> 00:20:01,890
Stop. You make it sound like
I'm the hero of the Colosseum.

287
00:20:01,890 --> 00:20:04,940
You are the hero of the Colosseum.

288
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:06,750
Stop saying that.

289
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:08,320
Okay, I stop.

290
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:11,000
Alright, I admit it if you insist!

291
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:15,260
Yes, I am the hero of the Colosseum!

292
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:21,320
I brought it!

293
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,370
Doffy, it's that thing!

294
00:20:23,370 --> 00:20:24,780
You're too close!

295
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:27,240
Too close but?

296
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,810
But I like it. Sit down.

297
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:38,810
If Straw Hat Luffy finds out about this,

298
00:20:38,810 --> 00:20:41,690
I'm sure he will try to get hold of it.

299
00:20:41,690 --> 00:20:45,560
An alliance can sometimes prove a hindrance.

300
00:20:46,470 --> 00:20:50,460
Diamante. I want to entrust this to you.

301
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:53,520
Wait a second, Doffy! I can't take it.

302
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:56,560
No, I want to entrust this to you.

303
00:20:56,560 --> 00:20:58,940
Stop. You make it sound like
I'm some kind of genius.

304
00:20:59,290 --> 00:21:02,940
I can only entrust this to a genius like you.

305
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:04,840
Stop saying that.

306
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:06,780
Okay, I stop.

307
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:10,630
Alright, I admit that I'm
a genius if you insist!

308
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:16,350
Yes! I can take care of
that dumb-ass Straw Hat!

309
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:21,450
I'll be counting on you!

310
00:21:21,450 --> 00:21:23,660
I know he will jump at it!

311
00:21:34,410 --> 00:21:38,710
The source of his late brother's power.
The Flare-Flare Fruit.

312
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:48,850
I'm sure he wouldn't want
anybody else to have it!

313
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,480
I see an island!

314
00:22:22,870 --> 00:22:24,460
I see it!

315
00:22:25,970 --> 00:22:29,390
The Straw Hats see a shadow of an island.

316
00:22:40,670 --> 00:22:43,310
What is that rocky island?!

317
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:59,590
We made it! It's Dressrosa!

318
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:03,530
You idiot! Don't shout!
Doflamingo will hear us!

319
00:23:03,530 --> 00:23:04,610
No, he won't!

320
00:23:04,610 --> 00:23:08,650
We'll save you soon, Kanjuro!

321
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:13,200
This is a kingdom of love
and passion - Dressrosa.

322
00:23:14,530 --> 00:23:16,370
I can't wait!
